periencePreferred Qualifications: Associate degree or above in Business Management or related field 1-2 years of appliance or premium brands experience Auto Req. ID392473BR Employment CategorySales Job LevelEntry Level Location Number000054-Mesquite-Store Address2701 N MESQUITE DR CityMesquite StateTX Apply to Job SEARCH CAREERS Search by keyword: Select a location: All locations Anchorage, AK Alabaster, AL Birmingham, AL Dothan, AL Florence, AL Fultondale, AL Hoover, AL Huntsville, AL Mobile, AL Montgomery, AL Oxford, AL Tuscaloosa, AL Benton, AR Conway, AR Fayetteville, AR Fort Smith, AR Hot Springs, AR Jonesboro, AR Little Rock, AR North Little Rock, AR Rogers, AR Avondale, AZ Chandler, AZ Flagstaff, AZ Gilbert, AZ Glendale, AZ Goodyear, AZ Mesa, AZ Oro Valley, AZ Phoenix, AZ Prescott, AZ Scottsdale, AZ Surprise, AZ Tempe, AZ Tucson, AZ Yuma, AZ Auburn, CA Bakersfield, CA Beaumont, CA Brentwood, CA Burbank, CA Canoga Park, CA Carlsbad, CA Cerritos, CA Chino, CA City Of Industry, CA Colma, CA Concord, CA Corona, CA Costa Mesa, CA Culver City, CA Daly City, CA Dinuba, CA Duarte, CA Dublin, CA El Cajon, CA El Centro, CA El Segundo, CA Elk Grove, CA Fairfield, CA Folsom, CA Fullerton, CA Goleta, CA Hawthorne, CA Huntington Beach, CA Irvine, CA La Jolla, CA Lakewood, CA Long Beach, CA Los Angeles, CA Marina, CA Menifee, CA Milpitas, CA Mission Viejo, CA Modesto, CA Montclair, CA Mountain View, CA Murrieta, CA National City, CA Northridge, CA Oakland, CA Oceanside, CA Orange, CA Oxnard, CA Pacoima, CA Pasadena, CA Pinole, CA Pleasant Hill, CA Rancho Cucamonga, CA Rancho Mirage, CA Redding, CA Redwood City, CA Riverbank, CA Riverside, CA Roseville, CA Sacramento, CA Salinas, CA San Bernardino, CA San Bruno, CA San Carlos, CA San Diego, CA San Francisco, CA San Jose, CA San Luis Obispo, CA San Marcos, CA San Rafael, CA Santa Ana, CA Santa Clara, CA Santa Clarita, CA Santa Maria, CA Santa Rosa, CA Santee, CA Sherman Oaks, CA Signal Hill, CA Simi Valley, CA Soquel, CA Sunn